# Collaboration Profile

Personal preferences and corrections that apply across all projects. This file is gitignored — it lives locally and accumulates over time.

Update this file when you notice patterns in how you prefer to work or when you correct Claude's behavior.

---

## Communication Style

- Concise responses — no filler, no trailing summaries
- Lead with the action or answer, not the reasoning
- Don't restate what I said — just do it
- Short, direct sentences

